機構聯防機制通報單影本1份（見偵249號卷第51頁）。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/111%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c2703%2c20220830%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,111,上訴,2703,20220830,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"2703","JDATE":"20220830","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}